OL,5, Paedophiles convicted of serious sexual
OL,6, offences could lose parental rights    
OL,7, over their children under a new law.   
OL,9,FThe proposed law change comes after the
OL,10,FBBC reported the case of a mother who  
OL,11,Fspent #30,000 in legal fees to stop her
OL,12,Fpaedophile ex-husband getting access to
OL,13,Ftheir daughter.                        
OL,15,FAfter hearing the story, Labour MP     
OL,16,FHarriet Harman tabled an amendment to  
OL,17,Fthe Criminal Justice Bill.             
OL,19,FIt covers the most serious sexual      
OL,20,Foffence - rape of a child under 13.    
